Package: atacInferCnv
Type: Package
Title: Call CNV from single cell ATAC-seq data based on InferCNV adaptation
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c( person("Konstantin", "Okonechnikov",email = "k.okonechnikov@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre")) )
Description: The package prepares input scATAC-seq data and adapts for copy number variance profiling with InferCNV package usage. It has also various paramters to control the analysis (e.g. external reference, metacellc, bin size, etc) and custom plot visualizations.   
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.0),utils
Imports: 
    infercnv (>= 1.3.1),
    Signac,
    Seurat,
    GenomicRanges,
    config,
    stringr,
    ggplot2,
    Rcpp,
    RcppEigen
biocViews: Epigenetics, Sequencing,  CopyNumberVariation,
        SingleCell,ImmunoOncology
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests: testthat, BiocStyle, knitr, rmarkdown
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
LinkingTo: 
    Rcpp,RcppEigen

